ompsignal " translate="no">P_24V_1</compsignal></comp>. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The Power supply is located in the Power box. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Dis-assembly</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><prereq id="GUID-F8EE43B1-36AF-4F86-8810-3B686A03AF19" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li id="LI_53184B16D403439F881DA2AB90C20E0F" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Power off the system</b>: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">On the operator panel, tap on the [System] icon on the right. Tap on [Power management]. Tap on [Power off]. The system shuts down. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Switch off the power supply</b>: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When the system has shut down, pull to open the cover under the roll winder. Switch the power switch to the 'off' position. 
</p></li><li id="LI_63A0C945A5EE411381005D65504AC5A8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Unplug the mains cables. 
</p></li><li id="LI_C2FA7457FFD3471487963362308437D9" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the power box. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="22DISA001" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-2AEF3168-FF41-4AB1-BE85-D47F0F71B408.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 22 How to remove the power box?>22 How to remove the power box</xref> 
